    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0843c21"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>五臺山清涼寺<persName key="A010378">道義</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0843c22"/><persName key="A010378">釋道義</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013661">江東衢州</placeName>人也。<date from-iso="0713" key="j19818371992113" to-iso="0742">開元</date>中至<placeName key="PL000000005250">臺山</placeName>，於<lb
ed="T" n="0843c23"/><placeName key="PL000000005373">清涼寺</placeName>粥院居止，典座普請運柴，負重登<lb
ed="T" n="0843c24"/>高，頗有難色。<persName key="A010378">義</persName>將竹鞋一緉轉貿人荷擔。<lb
ed="T" n="0843c25"/>因披三事納衣。東北而行，可五里來，於楞<lb
ed="T" n="0843c26"/>伽山<!--找不到此地-->下，逢一老僧，其貌古陋，引一童子名<lb
ed="T" n="0843c27"/>字<persName key="A011050">覺一</persName>。老僧前行，<persName key="A011050">童子</persName>呼請<persName key="A010378">義</persName>東邊寺內啜<lb
ed="T" n="0843c28"/>茶去，乃相隨入寺，遍禮諸院。見大閣三層，<lb
ed="T" n="0843c29"/>上下九間，總如金色，閃爍其目。老僧令遣<pb ed="T" n="0844a" xml:id="T50.2061.0844a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0844a01"/><persName key="A010378">義</persName>早還所止，山寒難住。唯諾辭出寺，行及<lb
ed="T" n="0844a02"/>百步，迴顧唯是山林，乃知化寺也。却回<placeName key="PL000000042189">長<lb
ed="T" n="0844a03"/>安</placeName>。<date from-iso="0766-12-22" key="j20011912001238" to-iso="0767-02-07">大曆元載</date>，具此事由奏<persName key="A004379">寶應元聖文武皇<lb
ed="T" n="0844a04"/>帝</persName>，蒙勅置<placeName key="PL000000005372">金閣寺</placeName>，宣十節度助緣<note resp="sgsz">此事另見《舊唐書．卷一百十八》《新唐書．卷一百四十五》。</note>。遂召<lb
ed="T" n="0844a05"/>蓋造都料，一僧名<persName key="A019455">純陀</persName>，為度土木，造<placeName key="PL000000005372">金閣<lb
ed="T" n="0844a06"/>一寺</placeName>。<persName key="A019455">陀</persName>元是西域那爛陀寺<placeName key="PL000000048273">喜鵲院</placeName>僧。<placeName key="PL000000005372">寺</placeName>成<lb
ed="T" n="0844a07"/>後，勅賜<persName key="A019455">不空三藏</persName>焉。<persName key="A010378">義</persName>不測其終。</p>
